### 2. Pipeline — "Research → Write" flow

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Reuse 100% downstream pipeline (Step 4-8). Chỉ thay thế Step 1-3.

#### Current Narrative Pipeline (8 steps):
```
Step 1: Concatenate source files          ← THAY THẾ
Step 2: Detect original framework         ← LOẠI BỎ (không có script gốc)
Step 3: Extract blueprint from text       ← THAY THẾ bằng Research
Step 3.5: Enrich blueprint                ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
Step 4: Select frameworks (AI ranking)    ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
Step 5: Generate outline                  ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
Step 6: Audit outline                     ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
Step 7: Write chapters                    ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
Step 8: Cross-chapter review              ← GIỮ NGUYÊN
```

#### Research → Write Pipeline (7 steps):
```
Step 1: Research blueprint (Plan A: 3 Flash + 3 Pro, parallel)  ← NEW
Step 2: Enrich blueprint (Google/AI)                             ← từ Step 3.5
Step 3: Select frameworks (AI ranking)                           ← từ Step 4
Step 4: Generate outline                                         ← từ Step 5
Step 5: Audit outline                                            ← từ Step 6
Step 6: Write chapters                                           ← từ Step 7
Step 7: Cross-chapter review                                     ← từ Step 8
```

